659
01:06:53,747 --> 01:06:55,749
DO YOU LIKE ME ?

660
01:07:04,758 --> 01:07:06,760
COME ON.

661
01:07:46,800 --> 01:07:48,302
DID YOU EVER...

662
01:07:48,802 --> 01:07:53,307
