GO BEHIND ME
A LONG TIME AGO.

675
01:10:07,691 --> 01:10:10,193
HEY.

676
01:10:27,210 --> 01:10:29,713
ALL RIGHT. 
YOU CAN RELAX NOW.

677
01:10:29,713 --> 01:10:32,716
