OFFICER TRAINING
WITH OLD CLAUDE.

695
01:11:31,775 --> 01:11:34,778
UH, OR KICK-ASS CLAUDE
AS THEY USED TO CALL HIM.

696
01:11:34,778 --> 01:11:37,280
SO HOW'S THE OLD MAN DOING
THESE DAYS ?

697
01:11:37,781 --> 01:11:41,785
