718
01:13:29,643 --> 01:13:31,645
SEE YOU TOMORROW,
OR YOU'RE FIRED.

719
01:13:39,152 --> 01:13:41,154
HEY !

720
01:13:43,657 --> 01:13:45,659
CIAO.

721
01:14:03,677 --> 01:14:06,429
