SURE.

727
01:14:52,475 --> 01:14:54,477
DOLPHIN ISLAND.
RIGHT HERE.

728
01:14:54,477 --> 01:14:56,479
I CAN TAKE YOUR BAG
FOR YOU.

729
01:14:56,479 --> 01:14:58,982
ALL RIGHT.
HAVE A GOOD TRIP.

732
